title: North Korea marks army anniversary with military parade
text:
North Korea marks army anniversary with military parade Thursday, February 08, 2018 - 01:27 
North Korea marked the founding anniversary of its army with a large military parade in Pyongyang. Kim Jong Un, in a black hat and matching coat, was in attendance. Rough cut (no reporter narration). ▲ Hide Transcript ▶ View Transcript
